highlights.text: XXXTENTACION has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “SAD!” is the highest at #7.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 67 weeks straight.
“Call Out My Name” by The Weeknd is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
“New Freezer (feat. Kendrick Lamar)” by Rich The Kid and Kendrick Lamar is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 63 spots at #97.
